      <title>dnsimpleでダイナミックDNSをつかう</title>
      <link>http://mojavy.com/blog/2014/12/23/dnsimple-dynamic-dns/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Dec 2014 20:02:30 JST</pubDate>
